                    </div>
                    <span>Even as an experianced Java programmer, I had hard time following the examples using Java in this book.<p>Some example codes in the book are missing in the download.<br>So I had to type them in myself only to find the examples in the book are not working.<p>This book is so poorly organized that I can't help but to suspect that it might have been written by more than one author in a hurry.<p>As an example, at one point the book was dicussing accessing the servlet in JRun and then ran the demo in Resin.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Not this desperate</div>
