                    </div>
                    <span>I was very impressed with this book, it gives a solid foundation to flash remoting, it doesn't matter if you use CF , J2EE, or .net it is all covered nicely.<p>I am very happy that it is not just a do this then this then this and you get this, but it goes into the why you did that to get that, not many books I have do that.<p>It even includes 3 of the most sought after applications involving online presence, the message board the email client as well as teh ecommerce solution.<p>This book is a '+' if you are wanting to get into flash remoting then this is the difinitive guide.</span>
                  
              
